<http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3734.2.7>
    bibo:endPage "240" ;
    bibo:issue "2" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:startPage "221" ;
    bibo:volume "3734" ;
    dc:creator "Wasonga, Domnick V.; Channing, Alan" ;
    dc:date "2013" ;
    dc:title "Identification of sand frogs (Anura: Pyxicephalidae: Tomopterna) from Kenya with the description of two new species" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.220048>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.220049>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.220046> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.220048>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Tomopterna wambensis sp. nov. from Wamba, Kenya. Dorsolateral views in life (A) NMK A / 5152 / 1, male and (D) A / 5152 / 5, female, dorsal views in alcohol, (B) A / 5152 / 1, male, and (C) A / 5152 / 5, female, ventral views in alcohol, (E) A / 5152 / 1, male and (F) A / 5152 / 5, female." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/220048/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.220049>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Chorus of Tomopterna gallmanni recorded at Laikipia, and a chorus of Tomopterna wambensis recorded at Wamba." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/220049/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.220046>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Map showing the sampled populations of Tomopterna species from Kenya. Type localities are marked by a circle - Laikipia Nature Conservancy (T. gallmanni sp. nov.) and a triangle - Wamba (T. wambensis sp. nov.). T. cryptotis populations are shown by solid squares." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/220046/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

